01:22:37,141 --> 01:22:38,631
嘿
Hey.

1493
01:22:38,809 --> 01:22:40,504
你好吗？
How you doing?

1494
01:22:41,846 --> 01:22:43,541
我是凯文
Kevin.

1495
01:22:45,049 --> 01:22:46,744
威尔海约
Will Hayes.

1496
01:22:47,451 --> 01:22:50,215
我只是在等艾波
I'm just waiting for April.

1497
01:22:52,223 --> 01:22:55,818
你是她前阵子提的凯文吗？
Are you the same Kevin that she mentioned a while back?

1498
01:22:54,720 --> 01:22:55,803
(PHONE RINGING)

1499
01:22:55,893 --> 01:22:58,691
希望是罗，  除非她是在收集叫凯文的
I hope so. Unless she's collecting Kevins.

1500
01:22:58,763 --> 01:23:00,890
凯文，  电话！
OLIVIA: Kevin, phone!

1501
01:23:00,965 --> 01:23:04,958
我满确定我是唯一跟她同居的凯文
Anyway, I'm pretty sure I am the only Kevin who's actually living with her.

1502
01:23:44,141 --> 01:23:46,302
你知道你要什么了吗？
Do you know what you want yet?

1503
01:23:46,977 --> 01:23:48,842
-不 -不？
-No. -WAITRESS: No?

1504
01:23:54,552 --> 01:23:56,179
威尔？
Will?

1505
01:23:56,654 --> 01:23:58,417
威廉海约？
William Hayes?

1506
01:23:58,489 --> 01:24:00,389
天啊
God.

1507
01:24:00,458 --> 01:24:02,426
-是你！ -夏曼
-It is! -Summer.

1508
01:24:03,027 --> 01:24:04,790
你好美
You look beautiful.

1509
01:24:05,596 --> 01:24:08,793
