-喂 -喂，  我是威尔
-Hello. -Hey, it's Will.

1623
01:31:04,414 --> 01:31:07,178
我很抱歉弄掉你的电话
I'm really sorry I lost your number.

1624
01:31:08,418 --> 01:31:12,115
我刚刚突然有好奇怪的画面闪过
I just had the weirdest flash of a whole life,

1625
01:31:12,189 --> 01:31:14,521
从未发生的画面
one that never, ever happened.

1626
01:31:17,494 --> 01:31:19,519
我们怎么了？
What did happen to us?

1627
01:31:19,596 --> 01:31:21,587
你跟我的室友上床
-You slept with my roommate. -Oh!

1628
01:31:22,799 --> 01:31:24,130
抱歉
I'm sorry.

1629
01:31:24,201 --> 01:31:26,965
没记错的话 是我的“计划”不是吗？
If I remember correctly, I believe it was my "plan," wasn't it?

1630
01:31:27,037 --> 01:31:28,800
-那计划，  还记得吗？ -对，  计划
