and then after we broke up, I just felt lost.

1634
01:31:41,018 --> 01:31:45,921
我还是感到很迷失，  尤其在谈感情时
I still feel pretty lost, especially when it comes to relationships.

1635
01:31:47,090 --> 01:31:48,580
嗯
Yeah.

1636
01:31:49,259 --> 01:31:51,750
嗯，  我也…我也是
Yeah, I've been... Me, too.

1637
01:31:58,168 --> 01:32:00,898
你有没有想过
Did you ever think

1638
01:32:01,538 --> 01:32:04,974
或许我们需要的 只是一个不同的计划？
that maybe we just needed a different plan?

1639
01:32:05,943 --> 01:32:08,912
等等！停止！倒回去
Wait! Stop! Stop right there. Now, go back.

1640
01:32:08,940 --> 01:32:10,024
(REWINDING)

1641
01:32:10,080 --> 01:32:12,810
好，  停，  慢速往前
Okay, stop. Now go forward, slowly.

1642
01:32:13,650 --> 01:32:15,174
就是这里
Now here it comes.

1643
01:32:15,252 --> 01:32:17,220
那里！就是那里！
There! Right there!

1644
01:32:17,387 --> 01:32:19,617
就是那个！ 我就是因为那个才猜到的！
That's it! That's how I figured it out!

1645
01:32:19,690 --> 01:32:21,453
我每次不开心时妈都会那样做
That's what Mom does when I'm upset.

1646
01:32:21,525 --> 01:32:24,119
她会摸摸我的头发，要我变得很棒
She fluffs up my hair and tells me to be brilliant

1647
01:32:24,194 --> 01:32:27,129
或是像太阳一样耀眼 每次都让我觉得好多了
or shine like the sun, and it always makes me feel better.

1648
01:32:27,197 --> 01:32:29,461
-听来像是个好母亲 -她是很棒的母亲
-Sounds like a great mom. -She is a great mom.

1649
01:32:29,533 --> 01:32:36,029
所以你百分百确定艾蜜莉 就是现在朝我们走过来
So you're absolutely positive, 100%, that Emily is the very same woman

1650
01:32:36,406 --> 01:32:38,601
的那个女人？
walking toward us right now?

1651
01:32:40,010 --> 01:32:41,637
绝对是
Absolutely.

1652
01:32:41,845 --> 01:32:43,472
是吗？
Is it?

1653
01:32:45,115 --> 01:32:47,379
-妈！妈！ -嘿！
-Mom! Mom! -Hey!

1654
01:32:51,054 --> 01:32:52,544
我好高兴是你
I'm so glad it's you.

1655
01:32:52,623 --> 01:32:55,183
-不然是谁？ -谁都不是
-Well, who else would it be? -Nobody.

1656
01:32:56,126 --> 01:32:58,458
-早安，  威尔 -嘿，  莎拉
-Good morning, Will. -Hey, Sarah.

1657
01:32:59,463 --> 01:33:01,931
妈，  爸可以跟我们一起来吗？
Mom, can Dad come with us to the zoo?

1658
01:33:01,999 --> 01:33:04,229
可以啊，  若爸爸想来的话
Yeah, if Dad wants to come, sure.

